{"tid":2272445,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警漏錄供詞 稱返工身心疲累","createTime":"2020-11-05T05:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T10:06:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"945fd8e4bd5d2d3573c1d839bb3b611b3bace138","tid":2272445,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T05:20:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/7JUA2V63NRHTJA4VPHY22YABIA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2F7JUA2V63NRHTJA4VPHY22YABIA%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4FQKcmgIyYy1b1J%2Bn%2Bjwg5M%3D&h=7dd38e7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2F7JUA2V63NRHTJA4VPHY22YABIA%2F&h=8de22bad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/7JUA2V63NRHTJA4VPHY22YABIA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警漏錄供詞 稱返工身心疲累<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_ggQ2Ty2xxllep4ImVKhz1kBcjE=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WBYEKYTWZBB4ZKLGQNF7NRYFUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_ggQ2Ty2xxllep4ImVKhz1kBcjE%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWBYEKYTWZBB4ZKLGQNF7NRYFUY.jpg&h=0ad76eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防暴警陳智勇<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年11月中環快閃和你Lunch期間，警方在交易廣場制服並拘捕多人，一名35歲司機被指襲警、非法集結及身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品。司機昨受審前承認襲警罪，但否認餘下兩罪。警員供稱，聚集者情緒不穩不停辱罵「黑警死全家」，其中被告走在群眾最前線指罵，但他接受盤問時承認聽不到被告說甚麼；又承認漏錄供詞，解釋因連續幾天工作逾十二小時，身心疲累，望法庭原諒。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警員3434陳智勇昨供稱，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯方：防暴扑頭拘被告<br />\n<br />\n陳續指當時群眾不理警告，續向警方掟雜物甚至衝前指罵，他遂揮動警棍驅散，惟被告反抗更欲搶去他手上的圓盾，他遂用警棍擊打被告的手驅趕。被告突然折返撞向A，陳上前支援，遭被告打中左胸。被告最後被壓在地上制服。<br />\n<br />\n陳接受盤問時承認，記事冊或口供紙中並無記錄部份庭上供詞，「由於我哋連續好多日返工超過12小時以上，身心好疲累，當我哋經過咁長時間工作，好疲倦，所以有啲口供遺漏咗，請法官閣下原諒。」<br />\n<br />\n陳承認當時現場嘈吵，聽不到被告舉起手說了甚麼，但堅稱被告在指罵警方。陳稱看不到有警員扑打被告至頭破血流，更否認警方對手無寸鐵的被告使用過份武力。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC2567/19"},{"pid":"3fed6a888035ea8963d3ec672eef5c6cd888f2bb","tid":2272445,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T05:25:50.000Z","msg":"Ok收到收到 即刻po ig story先👌🏻👌🏻"},{"pid":"8194b044072b8a309f749c59a33ad55c3a412044","tid":2272445,"uid":352936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"老細我過數比自己嗰陣打多左隻零，因為身心疲累<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d7810d690aa428e9c72964efca206f7dc28d39","tid":2272445,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"咁辛苦點解唔辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115ef06ec271aa3b8a84ee51f885a4e58af35bb5","tid":2272445,"uid":81657,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T05:58:55.000Z","msg":"屌，而家啲黑警渣架？又唔捱得，做野超過12個鐘就呱呱嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想當年我通宵咗成晚第二間開完早會再同埋個客簽約，30幾個鐘先睏粒聲都無出過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff59b6e40612fe1ca9da571cceb6dd78b73bacb","tid":2272445,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:14:27.000Z","msg":"醫生錯誤割除春袋致病人不育 稱返工身心疲累"},{"pid":"f5722d38e5d4ea1717b4e4c77b4564ee87007b70","tid":2272445,"uid":364770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"佢返工一定冇糧出"},{"pid":"4fcae666f85ed4a1d3ebbad86993d262a031153e","tid":2272445,"uid":65604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"依個警察唔掂，做錯嘢咪做錯嘢囉，俾假口供都大把，又點？你希望法庭諒咩解，講到法院可以制衡警察咁，做壞規矩喎，有無mon post 阿sir，強烈要求依個作供警紀律處分。"},{"pid":"894f4a7b8429cc553639cf772ef7b28574a1c60b","tid":2272445,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:14:01.000Z","msg":"又話有隨身鏡頭？乜唔係一開工就要開着？"},{"pid":"d45ad799d5856faff1dee4486f50a33d1097e9e3","tid":